  <original-body>ActiveSupport should allow dynamic cache store initialization just how database adapters work:

    config.cache_store = :foo_store

If :foo_store is not recognized, AS should try to require the convention:

    require 'active_support/cache/foo_store'

I'm working on a next gen memcached client, [Dalli](http://github.com/mperham/dalli), and this would make Dalli a drop-in replacement for memcache-client but the user does need to require the store adapter currently:

    require 'active_support/cache/dalli_store'
    config.cache_store = :dalli_store

I will create a patch later this weekend.</original-body>
